  "generation_notes": "Professional services SOW. Use deliverables-oriented language. Do not invent scope items not in user input. Keep timeline realistic — if start and end dates are given, surface the duration. If assumptions is empty, generate a conservative default set (client responsiveness, access to systems, out-of-scope items)."
